      <div class="about-section">
        <div class="about-section-title">📌 Riwayat Update</div>
        <div class="about-changelog">
          <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v1.0.0</span> — GP45 DB Edition<br>
      • Database 41.101 item + outlet stock 35.314 item (bawaan)<br>
