          <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.9.0</span> — Scanner Fix: FPS Turun, Res Naik, Focus Continuous<br>      • FPS 15 → 8 biar tiap frame lebih terang & kurang noise<br>      • Resolusi 640×480 → 1280×720 biar detail bar barcode lebih kebaca<br>      • Tambah focusMode continuous biar kamera auto fokus<br>      • Fix: barcode CODE-128 tipis & bengkok lebih gampang terdeteksi<br>      <br>
          <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.8.0</span> — Scanner Cepat + Remove QR<br>      • FPS 5 → 15 biar scan lebih responsif dan cepat<br>      • Hapus QR_CODE (gak dipake di toko)<br>      • Hapus qrbox (cuma buat QR)<br>      <br>          <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.7.1</span> — Torch Fix - native API<br>      • Torch sekarang pake native MediaStreamTrack API biar bisa nyala<br>      <br>          <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.7.0</span> — Orange Theme + Torch + Scanner Overlay<br>      • Ganti semua warna merah jadi orange (header, tombol, harga, dll)<br>      • Tombol Flashlight/Lampu di scanner (nyala/mati)<br>      • Scanner pindah ke overlay panel (gak ganggu halaman)<br>      <br>          <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.6.0</span> — 3-Button Lantai Setting + Scanner Beep<br>      • Setting lantai pake 3 tombol langsung (L1 | L2 | Nonaktif)<br>      • Scanner tambah beep & vibrate biar tau scan berhasil<br>      • Perbaiki layout omset percentage pake badge box<br>      <br>          <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.5.0</span> — Scanner Fix Lag + All Barcode Format<br>      • Camera FPS turun 5 biar ringan di HP<br>      • Resolusi kamera 640x480 biar gak lag<br>      • Barcode formats lengkap: CODE_128, CODE_39, EAN_13, EAN_8, UPC_A, UPC_E, QR<br>      • facingMode environment (tanpa exact) biar kompatibel semua device<br>      • Hapus torch & fallback yang bikin ribet<br>      <br>      <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.4.0</span>nel<br>      <br>      <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.2.0</span> — Fix Omset Detail Click Bug<br>      • Perbaiki bug klik detail sales hapus row lain<br>      <br>      <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.1.0</span> — Omset Code Cleanup<br>      • Hapus dead code renderOmset + tryJson<br>      • Bersihin duplicate render logic<br>      <br>      <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v4.0.0</span> — STABLE: Price Card fix + Detail Panel overlay + ULTIMATE badge<br>      • Price Card crash fix (findIndex + .finally compatibility)<br>      • Detail Price Card pake overlay panel sendiri<br>      • Badge ULTIMATE di icon original<br>      • Package: moorspangalila.ultimate.fresh (test)<br>      <br>      <span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)">v3.2.0</span> — Search Icon + Harga Hero + Bersihin Code<br>
          • 🔍 Search icon tetap di kiri, hapus emoji placeholder<br>
